episodes.name: Pacific Ditching (Transair Flight 810)
episodes.overview: The pilots of a crashed cargo jet believe they lost both engines. But when the wreckage emerges from the Pacific, the evidence tells another story.

episodes.name: Running on Empty (Air Tahoma Flight 185)
episodes.overview: An Air Tahoma cargo plane is within sight of a Cincinnati runway when both engines flame out and the turboprop crashes into a golf course.

episodes.name: Power Struggle
episodes.overview: Power Struggle: Sriwijaya Air Flight 182 crashed in to the Java Sea after a hard left bank, revealing deadly defects in the investigation that followed.

episodes.name: Second Thoughts (Luxair Flight 9642)
episodes.overview: Amid heavy fog and a rushed approach, Luxair Flight 50 falls out of the sky just a few miles short of Luxembourg airport.

episodes.name: Powerless Plunge (Loganair Flight 670A)
episodes.overview: Just moments after takeoff, a Loganair cargo flight from Edinburgh loses both engines and crashes into the icy North Sea

episodes.name: Cabin Chaos
episodes.overview: Cabin Chaos: After a Chinese airplane lands at a top-secret US Air Force base, the search is on for the cause of a deadly rollercoaster ride in the sky.

episodes.name: Deadly Climb (Midwest Express Airlines Flight 105)
episodes.overview: It's 1985-the deadliest year in civilian aviation-and a DC-9 commuter plane crashes just seconds after takeoff from Milwaukee.

episodes.name: Firebomber Down
episodes.overview: Firebomber Down: A C-130 firebomber crashes while battling an epic Australian wildfire. And ATSB investigators must determine the cause within an active fire zone.

episodes.name: Collision Catastrophe (2002 Ãœberlingen mid-air collision)
episodes.overview: German investigators are stumped when two planes collide while flying in the skies over southern Germany.

episodes.name: Fatal Test Flight (Airborne Express Flight 827)
episodes.overview: When a cargo plane test flight ends in disaster, investigators uncover a series of failures that doomed the DC-8 before it got off the ground.

episodes.name: No Exit (US Air 1493)
episodes.overview: Following a catastrophic runway collision at LAX, passengers on USAIR Flight 1493 struggle to escape the burning plane.
